  "1284190": {
    "name": "星球工匠",
    "steam_appid": 1284190,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284190/extras/98bd32901ebbb27094ba70289b6ca5c2.poster.avif?t=1763396816\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284190/extras/98bd32901ebbb27094ba70289b6ca5c2.webm?t=1763396816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在被投放到一个荒芜外星球后，你将会开启以下的旅途， </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独自探索或者与一群人一起改造整颗星球</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择独自探索，或与伙伴携手合作，在一颗神秘而荒芜的星球上共同建设、探索与改造。通过分工协作，你们可以同步推动环境变化，见证天空变蓝、湖泊形成、生机蔓延的全过程。独立的冒险会带来成就感，而团队的共同创造则会带来不一样的创作体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284190/extras/334be60a6b628312193f87232248fee2.poster.avif?t=1763396816\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284190/extras/334be60a6b628312193f87232248fee2.webm?t=1763396816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284190/extras/334be60a6b628312193f87232248fee2.mp4?t=1763396816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索，采集，自由建造，打造理想的外星球基地</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采集各种金属以及特殊资源、制造设备和生存工具、规划结构。从功能区到装饰布局，基地的每个细节都由你决定。你可以在任何的海拔或地貌建造自己的据点，让它既实用又独特，成为这颗星球上最温暖和独具匠心的基地。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284190/extras/0b7064ac9756849e7e2db60c5d1ead43.poster.avif?t=1763396816\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284190/extras/0b7064ac9756849e7e2db60c5d1ead43.webm?t=1763396816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284190/extras/0b7064ac9756849e7e2db60c5d1ead43.mp4?t=1763396816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >从荒芜之地开始，改造环境，唤醒星球生命</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着科技的进步，你将逐步改变大气成分、气候与生态系统，让一片死寂的荒原重新焕发生命。每一个阶段的变化都可被亲眼见证。从第一缕氧气，到第一片绿洲，再到星球被植被覆盖的那一刻。通过解码、混合 DNA 提取片段，创造新的生物。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284190/extras/d0526ae0c2e67610ca9ca1ee7ee00747.poster.avif?t=1763396816\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284190/extras/d0526ae0c2e67610ca9ca1ee7ee00747.webm?t=1763396816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284190/extras/d0526ae0c2e67610ca9ca1ee7ee00747.mp4?t=1763396816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无战斗威胁，专注且放松的探索与创造体验</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中没有敌人或外部威胁，只有来自&quot;大自然&quot;的挑战，你可以按照自己的节奏，享受采集、建造与探索的过程。这里没有紧迫的生存压力，只有从无到有的创造满足与静谧的美感。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284190/extras/cbfc26a0ff347e66f836ed0cf2d352a7.poster.avif?t=1763396816\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284190/extras/cbfc26a0ff347e66f836ed0cf2d352a7.webm?t=1763396816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284190/extras/cbfc26a0ff347e66f836ed0cf2d352a7.mp4?t=1763396816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随心调整挑战，按自己的节奏进行游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以选择轻松模式，纯粹体验改造的乐趣；也可以挑战更严苛的生存设定，考验策略与效率。无论偏好放松还是硬核，每位玩家都能找到适合自己的方式去建设这个新世界。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最后，除以上的几点之外，还有关于这颗星球与&quot;哨兵公司&quot;以及&quot;卫族&quot;的神秘故事等你去探索… </p>",
